    "body": "fixes #24928 \r\n\r\nClingo install Python extensions in non-standard locations and after #24095 this causes issues on some platforms. This PR:\r\n- [x] Add a default `site_packages_dir` property at the package level for each `PythonPackage`\r\n- [x] Override that property for `clingo-bootstrap`\r\n- [x] Add a new workflow to test bootstrapping on different operating systems\r\n",
